     H            Y.
     F** UTLR02M ********************************************
     F*  MERGE YYYY,MM,DD TO DATE (YYYYMMDD)                *
     F*  JW  2026.02.04                                     *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR02M'
     F*                    PARM           $YY     40
     F*                    PARM           $MM     20
     F*                    PARM           $DD     20
     F*                    PARM           $YMD    8
     F*  IN   $YY   : 4,0 YEAR
     F*  "    $MM   : 2,0 MONTH
     F*  "    $DD   : 2,0 DAY
     F*  OUT  $YMD  :  8A DATE (YYYYMMDD)
     F*******************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 @DATE
     I                                        1   4 @YY
     I                                        5   6 @MM
     I                                        7   8 @DD
     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $YY     40
     C                     PARM           $MM     20
     C                     PARM           $DD     20
     C                     PARM           $YMD    8
      *
     C                     MOVEL$YY       @YY
     C                     MOVEL$MM       @MM
     C                     MOVEL$DD       @DD
     C                     MOVEL@DATE     $YMD
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
